      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Layer 1 (Network): Power BI connects through a VNet Data Gateway injected into a delegated\nsubnet. Traffic flows over a Private Endpoint to the Databricks control plane, then through\nthe SCC relay to cluster nodes. All traffic stays on the Azure backbone.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Layer 1 (Network): Power BI connects through a VNet Data Gateway injected into a delegated\nsubnet. Traffic flows over a Private Endpoint to the Databricks control plane, then through\nthe SCC relay to cluster nodes. All traffic stays on the Azure backbone.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "aG"
    },
