      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Layer 2 (Authentication): A service principal replaces PATs. No user tokens involved.\nThe SPN is auditable, rotatable, and scoped. Entra ID Conditional Access policies apply.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Layer 2 (Authentication): A service principal replaces PATs. No user tokens involved.\nThe SPN is auditable, rotatable, and scoped. Entra ID Conditional Access policies apply.",
