      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Layer 3 (Authorization): Unity Catalog enforces least-privilege. The service principal only\ngets SELECT on specific tables. A dedicated SQL Warehouse separates BI from engineering compute.\nThis walks through the process from Power BI query to data access.  This follows the network path defined in Layer 1.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Layer 3 (Authorization): Unity Catalog enforces least-privilege. The service principal only\ngets SELECT on specific tables. A dedicated SQL Warehouse separates BI from engineering compute.\nThis walks through the process from Power BI query to data access.  This follows the network path defined in Layer 1.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "ac"
    },
